Staff are helpful and friendly
The staff are friendly and helpful - Ms. Lien. The breakfast is also good here. There are many varieties of food, Chinese, Vietnam and Western. I love the vietnam noodle the best. The view at night is beautiful if there is no fog. It really depends on your luck. We would recommend it to our friendd.
