Madelineen wrote a review Oct 2018
1 contribution
Wonderful location
We stayed in the ocean view suite for 3 nights for a second time and once again, the room was great and very spacious with wonderful beachfront views. The rooftop pool and bar was opened to the public, so you can come and enjoy one or two drinks here. The pool was peaceful and relaxing and we could find a free lounge to tan. We had ordered room service for lunch and had a very good, authentic and affordable meal. We also bought spa packages which was pleasant and relaxing for our family. All in all, our stay was wonderful and we'll sure be staying here again next time.
Date of stay: May 2018
